>\n例如:繳稅通知書、徵收差餉及∕或地租通知書、償還學生貸款通知書 ;<br />\n5. 本地大學或可頒授學位的高等教育院校發出的文件或收費單 ;<br />\n6. 由稅務局加蓋釐印的有效租約 ;<br />\n7. 下列公營機構發出的收費單、通知書或其他文件 :<br />\n&bull; 醫院管理局<br />\n&bull; 香港房屋委員會<br />\n&bull; 香港房屋協會<br />\n&bull; 香港考試及評核局<br />\n8. 下列機構發出的收費單、通知書或其他文件 :<br />\n&bull; 快易通(Autotoll)<br />\n&bull; 在港供應車輛用汽油∕柴油∕石油氣公司<br />\n&bull; 指定駕駛學校(包括:香港駕駛學院及觀塘駕駛學院)<br />\n&bull; 國際慈善機構(例如:聯合國兒童基金會)<br />\n&bull; 本地註冊的慈善機構(例如:香港公益金)<br />\n9. 有全名的屋苑住戶證<br />\n10. 有屋苑或屋村全名的居民協會會員證"},{"pid":"5963c0559df6e7766a5d058600c07e9898852d48","tid":2102480,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:23:41.000Z","msg":"一定要 投票大家加油"},{"pid":"b2920e6477235b6fe2b93f948eeafccd24631461","tid":2102480,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1zBrdj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1zBrdj.png&h=dc3b6e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順便幫手 Share：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkfactcheck.io/posts/318029346266274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fposts%2F318029346266274&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=42c73236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkfactcheck.io/posts/318029346266274</a>"},{"pid":"361409f2ab8de92881e9cb62514b39818838b5c6","tid":2102480,"uid":200792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:20:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9dd7a11d844fd3fe9566c39b3371baf54a84638d","tid":2102480,"uid":200792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a83a609eeb37ca603b0791549dd5625c729ca9b2","tid":2102480,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T23:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5BEefT0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5BEefT0.png&h=254e7f55&s={S